33:14.114 --> 33:20.841
♪♪

33:20.841 --> 33:27.608
♪♪

33:27.608 --> 33:34.174
♪♪

33:34.174 --> 33:36.056
‐I'm very sorry, ma'am.
It's a terrible loss.

33:36.056 --> 33:37.778
‐Yeah.

33:37.778 --> 33:46.947
