35:05.626 --> 35:07.708
‐One of these days,
you're gonna tell me...

35:07.708 --> 35:15.996
♪♪

35:15.996 --> 35:18.759
...why you want to touch God.

35:18.759 --> 35:22.843
♪♪

35:22.843 --> 35:24.725
You don't believe in God.

35:24.725 --> 35:27.848
♪♪

35:27.848 --> 35:29.369
You want to <i>be</i> God.

35:29.369 --> 35:31.411
‐Forward, top speed.

35:31.411 --> 35:38.418
♪♪

