36:35.716 --> 36:37.638
‐Hey.

36:44.244 --> 36:46.527
You ‐‐ You kept my hand ID
in the door.

36:48.609 --> 36:50.731
[ Dog barks ]

36:54.935 --> 36:57.738
[ Microwave hums ]

36:57.738 --> 36:59.740
[ Beeping ]

36:59.740 --> 37:02.503
[ Microwave door opens, closes ]

37:05.946 --> 37:07.908
I was at this guy's place.

37:07.908 --> 37:10.791
We had it on, you know,
on the TV.

37:17.998 --> 37:20.080
For a second, I was like...

37:26.727 --> 37:30.090
Thought about Mom.

37:30.090 --> 37:33.293
About when ‐‐
when we would watch

37:33.293 --> 37:35.976
and how scared we'd get
when you...

37:42.422 --> 37:48.388
Even for a second, I was like,
"What if he's gone?"

37:54.715 --> 37:58.438
Like, not ‐‐ not the thing,
but just, like...

38:01.962 --> 38:04.044
Like, if you were gone...

38:08.488 --> 38:11.211
...I wouldn't even know.

38:12.613 --> 38:14.134
‐You're high.

38:16.817 --> 38:19.179
Whose place?

38:21.782 --> 38:22.943
‐What?

38:22.943 --> 38:25.586
‐Where you were at.

38:25.586 --> 38:28.669
‐Just a friend...sort of.

38:30.791 --> 38:32.913
Not really a friend, I guess.

38:32.913 --> 38:33.914
‐Hmm.

38:38.118 --> 38:41.762
I thought you'd left town.

38:41.762 --> 38:43.804
‐I've been back for a while.

38:52.332 --> 38:54.214
‐Gonna eat something?

39:01.782 --> 39:03.584
‐I shouldn't have come here.

39:07.748 --> 39:10.511
I don't feel good.

39:10.511 --> 39:12.593
[ Vomits ]

39:12.593 --> 39:16.356
[ Coughs ]

39:16.356 --> 39:19.800
